{"tid":2134702,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"美國議員候選人：龍珠Z這樣的色情動畫會讓兒童墮落","createTime":"2020-08-01T02:16:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T10:53:02.000Z","uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2cb32b6c546781434b2daaf1f0b41e8521affe68","tid":2134702,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T02:16:28.000Z","msg":"美國的議員候選人KW Miller通過推特發出了目前互聯網上存在&ldquo;大量的色情動畫&rdquo;的警告。在舉例的時候，《龍珠Z》被點名。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.dmzj.com/resource/news/2020/07/30/1596088377158900.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.dmzj.com%2Fresource%2Fnews%2F2020%2F07%2F30%2F1596088377158900.jpg&h=bed54900&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nKW Miller是佛羅里達州的議員，承諾會實現&ldquo;美國優先&rdquo;的政策，支持重建製造業和重要的基礎設施，讓公民重返工作崗位。KW Miller表示：目前網絡上流傳著大量的色情動畫。其中《龍珠Z》的問題最大。他們用動畫角色進行性方面的描寫，想讓孩子們墮落。在一步該怎麼辦？何時會終結呢？<br />\n<br />\n對於KW Miller的發言，有網友在下面回復稱：不理解為什麼要舉《龍珠Z》作為例子，不知道是不是把一些同人作品中的內容和原作混淆了。"},{"pid":"675191da6c651d8e6201d650c20861bf1506a031","tid":2134702,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T02:18:02.000Z","msg":"幾時輪到龍珠，係都講Trouble啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdec304bd2d9735f144e145979da297d27374894","tid":2134702,"uid":97080,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T02:18:56.000Z","msg":"Dragon &quot;Ball&quot; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a88a1332c2400e50006dd39a687eaa35324b32d","tid":2134702,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"675191da6c651d8e6201d650c20861bf1506a031","tid":2134702,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T02:18:02.000Z","msg":"幾時輪到龍珠，係都講Trouble啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T02:19:29.000Z","msg":"屌記錯<br />\nTo Love-ru"},{"pid":"405515da93e4f915e23f2e2432442fd8cbc6d6ca","tid":2134702,"uid":11694,"